'''''Tjitji: Umukobwa wa Himba''''', ni filime ngufi ya Namibiya yasohotsemuri 2015 iyobowe na Oshosheni Hiveluahkandi yakozwe na Virginia Witts.  Iyi filime yibanze ku buzima bwa Tjijandjeua 'Tjitji', umunyeshuri ukiri muto, watsinze kandi wifuza cyane Himba ufite inzozi zâ€™ibanga zo kuzaba icyamamare 'Talk Show Host'. Iyi filime yamenyekanye kubera guca imyumvire ku bagore.   

Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime. Iyi filime yari ifite nomination mu byiciro Umuyobozi mwiza, Amashusho yumwimerere meza, amanota meza yumuziki wumwimerere, Cinematografi nziza, na Filime Nziza Nziza muri [[Namibian]] Theatre na Film Awards 2014 yabereye muri Theatre yigihugu ya Namibiya (NTN).  Nyuma, yatsindiye ibihembo bya cinematografi na firime yerekana inkuru muri Namibian Theatre na Film Awards muri 2014.  Yakiriwe neza mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Bangalore ryabereye i Bangalore, mu Buhinde mu 2015. ''Tjitji Umukobwa wa Himba na we'' yari filime ngufi ku mugaragaro mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Afurika muri 2015. 

